1. **Analyze and Describe the Main Target Image:**
   - **Count & Layers:** The main structure is composed of **12 blocks** and has **3 layers**.

      - **Layer 2 (Middle):** Two yellow semi-circular blocks are placed on top of the first two red arch blocks. A blue cube block is placed on top of the third red arch block. Two orange rectangular blocks are positioned on top of the last red arch block and the green rectangular block respectively.
      - **Layer 3 (Top):** Two yellow rectangular blocks are placed on top of the yellow semi-circular blocks. Two orange roof blocks are placed on top of the orange rectangular block and the blue cube block respectively.
